---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContentWithForm from '@layouts/sections/ContentWithForm.astro';
import Content from '@layouts/sections/Content.astro';
import Header from '@components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro';
import MapEmbed from '@components/MapEmbed.astro';

var campaignPhone = "215-316-5144"
---

<Layout title="Penn Radiology | Expert Imaging Close to Home">
    <Header href="#" campaignPhone={campaignPhone}>
        <p class="screen-reader-only">Penn Radiology - Expert Imaging Close to Home</p>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">Request Appointment</a></li>
                <li><a href="#services">Services We Offer</a></li>
                <li><a href="#locations">Locations</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </Header>
    <main>
        <ContentWithForm id="request-appointment" class="bg-white-to-blue" formId="45" formName="Radiology%20-%20Community">
            <hgroup slot="hgroup">
                <h1>Expert Imaging Close to Home </h1>
            </hgroup>
            <section slot="copy">
                <p>At Penn Radiology, you can get the care you need when you need it -- and close to home. </p>
                <hgroup>
                    <h2>Specialized Radiology Experts</h2>
                </hgroup>
                <p>Our expert radiologists offer the most advanced imaging services at 18 locations throughout the Philadelphia region. </p>
                <p>We also offer evening and weekend hours, and rapid results, so you can get the care you need as quickly as possible. </p>
                <hgroup>
                    <h3>Schedule Your Imaging Appointment</h3>
                    </hgroup>
                <p>To make an appointment with Penn Radiology call us at <a href="tel:2153165144">215-316-5144</a> or submit our form and we will call you back within one business day to help you schedule.
            </section>
            <hgroup slot="form-heading">
                <h3>Make an Appointment</h3>
            </hgroup>
        </ContentWithForm>
        <Content id="services" class="bg-blue-lightest">
            <hgroup>
                <h2>Radiology Services We Offer </h2>
            </hgroup>
            <p>Penn Radiology does more than 1 million diagnostic studies and therapeutic procedures each year. With among the most experience in the region, you can trust youâ€™ll receive an accurate diagnosis and greater peace of mind with your results.</p>
            <p>Our services include: </p>
            <ul class="two-columns">
                <li>3-D Mammography</li>
                <li>Bone Density Scan (Dexascan) </li>
                <li>Cardiac Calcium Scoring </li>
                <li>CT </li>
                <li>CT Angiography </li>
                <li>Low Dose CT Lung Screening </li>
                <li>MRI, Breast MRI, MRA </li>
                <li>Nuclear Medicine </li>
                <li>Plain X-Rays and Fluoroscopy (Using All Digital Equipment) </li>
                <li>Positron Emission Tomography (PET) </li>
                <li>Thyroid Biopsy </li>
                <li>Ultrasound </li>
                <li>Vascular </li>
            </ul>
        </Content>
        <Content id="locations" class="">
            <hgroup>
                <h2>Convenient Locations Close to You </h2>
            </hgroup>
            <p>Penn Radiology makes it easy to find an appointment in a location close to home and at a time that works best for you. </p>
            <p>Many of our 18 locations throughout the Philadelphia region offers evening and weekend hours and rapid results. </p>
            <MapEmbed src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/1/embed?mid=1WJspXoeez3hZf0m5mUR6UQ7bcXv2eEY&ehbc=2E312F">
            </MapEmbed>
        </Content>
    </main>
    <Footer target="#" class="" />
</Layout>